\title{W3 Constructions on Affine Lie Algebras}
\author{Source-backed arXiv sample}
\date{}
\begin{document}
\maketitle
\begin{abstract}
We use an argument of Romans showing that every Virasoro construction leads to realizations of \$W\_3\$, to construct \$W\_3\$ realizations on arbitrary affine Lie algebras. Solutions are presented for generic values of the level as well as for specific values of the level but with arbitrary parameters. We give a detailed discussion of the \$\textbackslash{}aff\{su\}(2)\_\textbackslash{}ell\$-case. Finally, we discuss possible applications of these realizations to the construction of \$W\$-strings.
\end{abstract}
